node.title: The hunt for Forrest Fenn's treasure
node.description: Forrest Fenn hid a treasure somewhere in the Rocky Mountains. Five men died searching for it.
node.content: ["Millionaire Forrest Fenn hid a treasure somewhere in the Rocky Mountains. Five men died searching for it.\u00a0", "\"48 Hours\" reveals new details, rarely seen photos and exclusive interviews in \"The Fenn Treasure.\"\u00a0"]
